28
00:02:24,908 --> 00:02:25,508
Rest assured.

29
00:02:25,709 --> 00:02:27,029
It's definitely going to work.

30
00:02:27,189 --> 00:02:29,028
Come on, repeat what I told you.

31
00:02:29,748 --> 00:02:30,228
Yeah.

32
