218
00:11:41,548 --> 00:11:42,108
Shifang.

219
00:11:43,629 --> 00:11:44,148
Yang.

220
00:11:44,949 --> 00:11:45,269
Shifang.

221
00:11:45,829 --> 00:11:47,788
